{"tid":2195092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BLM示威漸趨暴力, 打擊「拜登」選情","createTime":"2020-09-09T03:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T16:11:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fc017d0ff0b409e32f7751fcb2882a680730a9f5","tid":2195092,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:00:29.000Z","msg":"評論認為，其中一個原因是全美爆發示威浪潮初期，主流傳媒爭相報道和平遊行的新聞，種族關係問題也受到重視，因此提振了拜登的聲勢。但示威長期持續後，議題的熱度開始冷卻，共和黨保守派也繼續批評示威，因此情況出現了變化。<br />\n<br />\n統計顯示，美國人同情示威者以及認同BLM運動的程度越高，拜登的民望也相應上升。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有調查發現，美國人認為示威「大部份合理」的比例，已從6月的62%降至8月的53%，與此同時，認為示威者非法聚集的受訪者比例，則從6月的28%升至38%。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而在威斯康辛州，民意的變化比全國更加明顯</strong>。當地馬奎特大學（Marquette University）法學院的調查顯示，在6月至8月間，州內民眾對BLM運動的支持淨值，已從33個百分點滑落至10個百分點，對示威的支持淨值，也從27個百分點大減至負1個百分點。在這個背景下，拜登對特朗普的領先優勢，從8個百分點縮窄至4個百分點，由於4個百分點已在民調的誤差範圍內，因此也可說兩人其實是叮噹馬頭。<br />\n....<br />\n<strong>至於共和黨與特朗普方面，其中一個競選主軸就是恢復社會治安，所以基諾沙的示威變成騷亂後，有助特朗普指摘民主黨煽動暴力，自己才是維持秩序的領袖。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200905/XWQL3S4BAJHYBBTFLFMZDVXFN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200905%2FXWQL3S4BAJHYBBTFLFMZDVXFN4%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=7b58f601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200905%2FXWQL3S4BAJHYBBTFLFMZDVXFN4%2F&h=eb269369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200905/XWQL3S4BAJHYBBTFLFMZDVXFN4/</a>"},{"pid":"28dc6d801f877dc9e30381d6cb7257489cd8f829","tid":2195092,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672adb5092830abd07a26f15e0b4ca2933c773f4","tid":2195092,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:01:49.000Z","msg":"燈燈必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7333213c924ab5afbec6dc82e0235d5d4523fd5","tid":2195092,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"672adb5092830abd07a26f15e0b4ca2933c773f4","tid":2195092,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:01:49.000Z","msg":"燈燈必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4d10975e6a80c32333350e666df4679642f527","tid":2195092,"uid":151313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:03:02.000Z","msg":"Black Lives Better"},{"pid":"99038ea7442b42de0d4520f645800f1556dfa026","tid":2195092,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"拜燈一定無得輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcaa587e9cc0a2ac4a1110b7129a825fd1cbd2c","tid":2195092,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"拜登又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238a32915092427372905ca415f47a6210d1d0db","tid":2195092,"uid":273791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"亂咁quote新聞做標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人哋話倘若啊, 係分析嚟㗎"},{"pid":"afb87a06889a414864e87e468fe12ad6d5cc7bd4","tid":2195092,"uid":291526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20